<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-text" data-lang="text"><span class="line"><span class="ln">1</span><span class="cl">{{&lt; details &#34;More details&#34; &gt;}}
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="ln">2</span><span class="cl">&gt; The past is never dead. It&#39;s not even past.
