<h2 id="quote">Quote</h2>





<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-text" data-lang="text"><span class="line"><span class="ln">1</span><span class="cl">{{&lt; quote title=&#34;Requiem for a Nun&#34; author=&#34;William Faulkner&#34; ref=&#34;https://www.goodreads.com/work/quotes/2041161&#34; &gt;}}
